Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.71,0:07:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:20.04,spell,,0,0,0,,{\c&H25333B&\fs30\move(982.5,637.5,982.5,591,0,2654)\t(\fs33)}Niello Trade
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this is gonna be a blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.47,0:07:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Malga, aren't they holding a rising altitude race in the weighted atmosphere?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna enter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.26,0:07:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.53,0:07:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's enter one after work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We can make some money off the admirals and marines.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.67,0:07:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Malga, can you see Kimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She hasn't moved, so she's still in my sights.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that mean the chancellor hasn't budged?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.95,0:07:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure does. Care to make a comment?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.52,0:07:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a rush delivery for the student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:55.74,spell,,0,0,0,,{\c&H1D181B&\fs45\fax0.2\frz314.327\pos(1234.5,517.5)}Working Class Man
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The shipping label clearly says,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:08:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,"Highest Peak! The Virgin Queen Elizabeth, 1st Edition."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet the chancellor ordered this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to feel bad for him or make fun of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.72,0:08:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It was disguised as an educational program,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.74,0:08:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but he messed up the label.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So it seems...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Seijun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.49,0:08:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.46,0:08:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got back from Mikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Margot, is Masazumi there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.43,0:08:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him about the package and what's going on tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Seijun, the Chancellor's exorcising ghosts at school tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,See you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no, I live in Murayama,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.89,0:08:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'd have to go through the guard post to visit Okutama at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.48,0:08:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That would upset my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't your dad a big shot on the Provisional Council?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then this is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's addressed to the student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:52.76,hand,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord3.75\shad0\alpha&H40\3c&HD16870&\pos(546,18)\c&HFFFFFF&}{\p1}m 0 0 l 1065 0 1065 270 0 270{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:52.76,hand,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs57\fsp0.45\bord0\blur0.8\pos(31.5,15)}Musashi, Far East Okutama\NMusashi Ariadust Academy\NTo: Student Council\N\NLightning Delivery
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:52.76,hand,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs57\fsp0.45\bord0\blur0.8\pos(486,16.5)}Breakable!\N"Highest Peak! The Virgin Queen Elizabeth,\N1st Edition."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is this going to the student council?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The chancellor oughta be close to Remorse Way about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:08:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you should go see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.71,0:08:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, Seijun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A race!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, little missy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.23,0:09:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass that on to the chancellor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:17.20,date,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\an8\bord3\shad0\blur0.8\alpha&H30\c&H251F2A&\3c&H48E6F4&\pos(1647,91.5)}{\p1}m 0 0 l 465 0 465 270 0 270{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:16.45,date,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs48\bord0\shad0\blur0.8\c&H33DEEA&\pos(1647,124.5)\b1}Ritual Summons \NWork's Title \N"When One Falls Asleep" \NOperate 5 Times
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The chancellor and Kimi, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:47.77,date 2,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\fscx102\fscy110\blur20\c&HFFFFFF&\an9\fad(400,600)\pos(1713,650)}3:03 P.M. \N Musashi Ariadust Academy Student Dorms
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.31,0:09:47.77,date 2,,0,0,0,,{\fscx102\fscy110\blur1.6\1c&H899294&\an9\fad(400,600)\pos(1713,650)}3:03 P.M. \N Musashi Ariadust Academy Student Dorms
Dialogue: 2,0:09:45.31,0:09:47.77,date 2,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\fscx102\fscy110\blur1\an9\fad(400,600)\pos(1713,650)}3:03 P.M. \N Musashi Ariadust Academy Student Dorms
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You should come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's keeping you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.23,0:10:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, the Academy assigned me here as of today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.95,0:10:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I've never shared a room before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, it will be my first time with a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.32,0:10:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I-In that case—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just have to adjust.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.46,0:10:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you sure you don't mind living with a boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you leave if I asked?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,After you first arrived, you went and requested a different room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.11,0:10:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was rejected, so you've been standing outside the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you promise me something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We mustn't interfere with each other's personal affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.15,0:10:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,An extreme example would be
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.75,0:10:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that I couldn't complain even if you came back with a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.50,0:10:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.85,0:10:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm teasing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know who I admire?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,People who are dense, but earnest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't question those who are dense and earnest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.09,0:11:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You can come back if you're afraid,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,my silly brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.48,0:11:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You just had to destroy the mood right when it was getting good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.35,0:11:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's Tori doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that some new game?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Or should I go whack him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, I heard you were drinking in the cafeteria,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,so what brought you out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I just needed to cool off, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.72,0:11:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't use your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.28,0:11:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It will damage your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:11:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.73,0:12:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny, Teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, see,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.93,0:12:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I just remembered how an old lady in my neighborhood used to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, being drunk is no excuse for comparing me to an old woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.97,0:12:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it. You can...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.95,0:12:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, are you on my silly brother's side?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.61,0:12:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll always side with everyone in our class, not just Tori.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't interfere with any student affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.19,0:12:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Masazumi.
